Schedule of "round tables": July 27 at 18:30 - in the Karasun district at Selezneva Street, 244; July 28 at 18:30 - in the Central District at Stavropolskaya Street, 77; July 29 at 18:30 - in the Western District at Kalinin Street, 339; July 30 at 18:30 - in the Prikubansky district at at the address Atarbekov Street, 43.
